South African Gold Production Increased by 1.5% in April From Year Earlier

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-09T09:30:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/south-african-gold-production-increased-by-1-5-in-april-from-year-earlier.html
South African gold production rose
1.5 percent in April from a year earlier, Jean-Pierre
Terblanche, a spokesman for Statistics South  Africa , said by
phone from  Pretoria  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
